1. Mireil (The World's Mightiest Creature)
The game has a large story. It's not a small story that a team of adventurers and hunters will have to wait until a large number of people can see the world. Once they discover a world for them, a group of adventurers will discover a world for them as well. The game is the first to feature a story similar to the novel series in development by Alain.
